  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Read-only fields Amount, Asset and Recipient can be modified if return back after transaction was sent in chat\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nFields can't be modified or there is no Send transaction screen if tap back, so user needs to make new /send \r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nafter user sends 1 transaction in 1:1 chat and taps on 'Got it' she can return back to Sign transaction screen with device back button. On this screen read-only fields Amount, Asset and Recipient can be modified and new transaction can be sent. Unfortunately, 1:1 chat will show initial value and not the one used in transaction. \r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\nfrom 00:17 https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/8494723/sessions/4393959670/?accessToken=JUDd5PA90-3eZLP5RwANpW0twfk\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Open 1:1 chat\r\n- send 1 transaction, tap Got it\r\n- tap device back button. As a result, Send transaction screen is shown\r\n- Try to edit field Amount and send transaction\r\n- Check send message in 1:1 chat and transaction history for the actual amount sent\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: nightly build june 15 and PR build https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/4761#issuecomment-397216921\r\n* Operating System: Android \r\n",
